[*] df and du:
# du displays disk usage by directory while df displays disk uasge by partition

du - disk usage

$ du -sh dir					# shows disk usage with summary and human readable format
$ du -h --max-depth 2 dir			# use max depth 2 to look for max depth of 2 dir
$ du --max-depth 2 dir | sort -n		# go to 2 max depth for specified dir and sort them by number which is eventuakky their size

df

$ df			# disk usage
$ df -h

